name: Colored Dual Coil 510 Tank Cartomizer - 3ml
description:
Dual Coil 1.5 ohm pre-punched cartomizer
Tank holds 3ml of e-liquid
Polished aluminum end caps
Comes with drip tip
Easy to fill
Tank Filling Instructions:
Filling the tank is easy.  Remove the drip tip from the top.  Pull the cartomizer down from the bottom so that you can view the top of the cartomizer through the see through wall of the tank.  (You can turn the drip tip upside down and push the cartomizer down to get it started.)  Then hold the tank at an angle (like pouring a beer) and fill it without allowing juice to get inside the cartomizer.  A syringe or needle bottle may make it easier but pouring from a drip tip bottle is quite easy.
 
After you have the tank filled up with you juice, push the cartomizer back up and into place.  Then prime the cartomizer by filling it with juice and let it sit for a few minutes so that it can fully saturate and wick through.  Screw the tank onto e-cig, then insert the drip tip (if you insert the drip tip prior to putting the tank onto your battery, it might push the cartomizer out again.  Tanks work well on eGo batteries or any mod.
Sorry, but there is no warranty or replacement on atomizers, cartomizers, clearomizers or tanks.
